data.description: Price Improvement - Motivated Seller - Come check out this beautiful slice of heaven. Seller has an assumable VA loan with 2.2% interest (buyer must qualify for VA lending) This quiet cul-de-sac provides plenty of privacy while enjoying the wide open spaces and views. A Large .61 acre lot is in close proximity to BLM land and recreational outdoor activities. This home has an open concept living, dining, and kitchen area. A free standing propane stove keeps you cozy in the winter. Enjoy the vaulted pine tongue and grove ceiling and real wood accents. Go out the french doors in the kitchen to the partially covered deck and enjoy the sunsets and the deer that frequent the yard. This 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home provides plenty of options for sleeping arrangements, office space or craft rooms. Plus a large storage room in the basement. The laundry room has a commercial washer/dryer combo that is staying with the home as well as the triple queen bunk bed frame. New metal roof installed in 2021. Spacious 1 car garage, greenhouse, garden shed, garden area and mature trees. The location and the lot size make this home one of a kind!!  A wildlife haven. Sit back and watch the deer year round.
